name: Ossuary (itch) (Snopingas, RGeeK, Kababeri, Diagno)
description:
Little 5 minutes long game made for the Brackeys Game Jam 2021.2

Play as soul 6702 who has to stack Urns falling from the sky in the correct order while stuff are raining fiercely on him.

Features 3 levels with increasing difficulty.

Dev Team :

Nicolas Cadre : Programmer and Sound Designer
